      "element_id": "23be6345-66f5-49ee-9ec8-abe6231d861e",
      "data": {
        "element_type": "definition_box",
        "content": "练习题：\n\n一个直角三角形的两条直角边分别为 9 和 12，请问斜边是多少？\n\n💡 提示：想想常见的勾股数组……",
        "position": {
          "region": "center",
          "offset_x": 0,
          "offset_y": 0
        },
        "style": {
          "color": "yellow",
          "size": "large",
          "animation": "grow"
        },
        "narration": "这道题：直角边9和12，斜边是多少？提示：你见过这个勾股数组吗？试试看能不能直接看出来！",
        "metadata": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "event_type": "element_added",
      "timestamp": 1776690171.8562539,
      "element_id": "afb64786-41ad-44e6-8783-2a9b4f0dbf0c",
      "data": {
        "element_type": "text_block",
        "content": "答案揭晓：\n\n9² + 12² = 81 + 144 = 225\nc = √225 = 15\n\n你发现了吗？9-12-15 就是 3-4-5 同时乘以 3 得到的！\n所以只要记住 3-4-5，就能快速推出 6-8-10、9-12-15……",
        "position": {
          "region": "center",
          "offset_x": 0,
          "offset_y": 0
        },
        "style": {
          "color": "green",
          "size": "medium",
          "animation": "fade_in"
        },
        "narration": "答案是15！9方加12方等于81加144等于225，开根号等于15。发现了没？9-12-15就是3-4-5乘以3！记住3-4-5，就能推出一整串勾股数。",
        "metadata": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "event_type": "element_added",
      "timestamp": 1776690175.286874,
      "element_id": "d99d0fb5-118d-4c59-ade3-f46572960667",
      "data": {
        "element_type": "title",
        "content": "八、重要提醒",
        "position": {
          "region": "center",
